text: Muwafaq Hussein is a former Iraqi football midfielder who played for Iraq. Muwafaq played for the national team in 1986 . He coached Iraq at the 2013 FIFA U-17 World Cup. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Al-Shorta SC players Category:Al-Shorta SC managers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Iraqi football managers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
